text: The Liberal Party of Australia (Western Australian Division), commonly called the WA Liberals, is the Western Australian branch of the Liberal Party, a centre-right, liberal conservative political party in Australia. It is currently in Opposition. It forms the Coalition with the National Party. Its current leader is Libby Mettam and the deputy leader is Steve Thomas.
